						               													<description>With Peril Beneath the Desert! Take your CONGO Games into the Ancient Tombs of Egypt!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is the 19th Century. Africa lies scorched by conflicts between tribal warriors and professional soldiers. All the while, cunning explorers scour the ancient ruins for sacred relics and unguarded gold. Having explored all they dared of the deep Congo jungles, the powers in play turn their attention north to the Egyptian deserts... and the treasures (and horrors) that wait beneath!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This supplement for Studio Tomahawk's CONGO adapts the popular rules system for play in the ancient tombs beneath the deserts of the Sudan and southern Egypt.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Included:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Supplement Handbook (22pgs) - with Peril Beneath the Sands! Scenario rules and backstory, maps of the tombs, a new Mahdist Column faction, and more! &amp;#10;     Scenario Bulletin - printable and designed to fit with standard CONGO scenarios!&amp;#10;     &amp;quot;The Tombs&amp;quot; A New Dangerous Terrain Chart - featuring traps and perils from your favorite adventure stories!&amp;#10;     Interactable Terrain Chart - Pre-designed results for searching various objects in the tombs... what may be found, or awakened... &amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Turn your jungle-thrashing adventures to tomb-crawling treasure-hunts, and brave the ancient terrors guarding the riches of the Nameless Pharaoh! Enter the tombs...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Note: CONGO Base rules required to play Peril! Scenario.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
